no more sunsets is a 2006 american short documentary film starring former trucker shawn bridges and filmed by chip rosetti at the former 's request .   the 29-minute black-and-white film presents a warning to children about the drug meth by way of an object lesson : the ravage of bridges ' long-time meth use and its effects on his family .   at the time of filming bridges was near-catatonic , bedridden with a catheter and a feeding tube , dying at the age of 34 .   his father was quoted as saying that he had the body of a 70 - 80-old man .   shawn bridges used meth for most of his adult life , suffering his first heart attack at the age of 26 .   by the time he eventually quit , it became clear that the damage done was lethal .   he had intended the film to be shown at his local church ; instead , it sparked international attention and media coverage .   bridges died in late march 2007 , aged 35 .   at the time , rosetti stated that he had sold 500-600 copies and was planning on a sequel .